{% comment %}
  GuamPick — Shipping Included Badge
  
  사용법:
  1. Shopify Admin → Online Store → Themes → Edit code
  2. Snippets → Add new snippet → 이름: "shipping-badge"
  3. 이 코드 전체 붙여넣기 → Save
  
  4. 상품 카드 템플릿에 렌더링 추가:
     product-card.liquid (또는 card-product.liquid) 안에:
     {% render 'shipping-badge', product: product %}
  
  5. 상품 상세페이지에도 추가:
     main-product.liquid (또는 product-template.liquid) 안에:
     {% render 'shipping-badge', product: product %}
{% endcomment %}

{% if product.tags contains 'shipping-included' %}
  <div class="gp-shipping-badge">
    <span class="gp-shipping-badge__icon">🚢</span>
    <span class="gp-shipping-badge__text">Shipping Included</span>
  </div>
{% endif %}

<style>
  .gp-shipping-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 5px;
    background: #e8f8ee;
    border: 1px solid #b7e4c7;
    color: #1a7a3f;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    margin-top: 6px;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .gp-shipping-badge__icon {
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  /* 상품 카드용 (작게) */
  .card-wrapper .gp-shipping-badge,
  .product-card .gp-shipping-badge {
    font-size: 11px;
    padding: 3px 8px;
  }

  /* 상품 상세 페이지용 (조금 크게) */
  .product__info-wrapper .gp-shipping-badge,
  .product-single .gp-shipping-badge {
    font-size: 13px;
    padding: 5px 12px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
</style>
